input_config.human_message:
Create a focused blog outline based on these parameters:
1. Core Requirements:
- Draft text: {{draft_text}} 
- Word count limit: {{word_count}} 
- Blog type: {{blog_post_type}} 
- Primary keyword: {{primary_keyword}} 
- Secondary keyword: {{secondary_keyword}} 
- Awareness stage: {{awareness_stage}} 
2. Content Structure:
- Create an H1 title incorporating primary keyword
- Design 3-4 main sections (H2) with relevant subsections (H3)
- Include introduction and conclusion
- Add FAQ section (3-5 questions)
- Suggest one clear call-to-action
3. SEO Elements:
- Meta description (150-160 characters)
- Key semantic keywords
- Image placement suggestions
Output should be a clear, hierarchical outline that can be executed within the specified word count.
